Data processing

iris.area <- iris %>% 
mutate(Petal.Area = Petal.Length * Petal.Width, Sepal.Area = Sepal.Length * Sepal.Width) 
res <- iris.area %>% 
group_by(Species) %>% 
summarize(Petal.Area.avg = mean(Petal.Area), Sepal.Area.avg = mean(Sepal.Area)) %>% 
left_join(iris.area) # , by='Species'
## Joining by: "Species"
print(res)
